@page "/"

<PageTitle>Home</PageTitle>

<h1>Azunt.InstructionManagement</h1>

<p>
    This Azunt.Web project is included for quick Blazor Server CRUD testing.
    It uses EF Core In-Memory, so you can run the web project and test the <a href="/Instructions">Instructions</a> page without publishing the SQL Server database project.
</p>

<p>
    The reusable module still supports SQL Server through EF Core, Dapper, and ADO.NET for real application scenarios.
</p>
